Yves Barsacq https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Yves_Barsacq 0 Yves Barsacq (17 June 1931 – 4 October 2015) was a French film actor, who appeared in more than 150 films. He is the son of the French-Russian production designer Léon Barsacq and the nephew of the French theatre director André Barsacq.
